              </div>

      			  <div class="mentioned">
      			  <p id="media">Mentioned by <a href="https://type.today/ru/journal/cyr2019">type.today</a>, <a href="https://vc.ru/design/76838-logotip-servisa-arendy-kvartir-kvartiry-onlayn-v-stile-messendzhera-ot-studii-artemiya-lebedeva">vc.ru</a>, <a href="https://skillbox.ru/media/design/interview-danya-vidmich/">Skillbox</a> and <a href="https://stolik.mave.digital/ep-53">podcast "Sosedniy stolik"</a></p>
