  <p>Led and scaled the design function: planned sprints, prioritized workload, mentored mid-level designers, and drove cross-functional collaboration with editorial and marketing</p>
  <p>Owned communication design across key funnels — landing pages, campaigns, and merch (14 SKUs) — improving launch speed, brand consistency, and engagement (NPS, Brand Awareness, Trust)</p>
